OL,4,G2000FClassic Movies: Great Expectations
OL,5,     GNew. A look at the vivid '40s
OL,6,     Gadaptation of the Dickens classic
OL,7,     Gabout a poor young orphan who
OL,8,     Gbecomes a gentleman of means
OL,9,     Gthanks to a mysterious benefactor.
OL,10,G2100FWhat's New Pussycat?
